I'm almost got the 4 billion dollar scenario ready (new version of 
401), just working on fine tuning the amount of money to give as much 
as possible.  It's getting fun to have a team full of characters who 
are experience level 343 (except for the slime).  I estimate I'm about 
1/4 of the way to the point of maxing out experience points for the 
characters.

Of course, I'm getting concerned abotu one thing.  It appears that the 
con stat has more affect on health than the armor stat or it could be 
because the strength level is so high that the cons stat would have 
more impact than it normally would on health.
